{"tid":1441142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！逼廢老睇文宣","createTime":"2019-08-10T15:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:48:56.000Z","uid":294954,"like":189,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"685985baf57e9837a394b7e275e0f8485fa6ef51","tid":1441142,"uid":294954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"引用一位巴打的post: <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434184</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋係幾個廢青，今日得閒冇事就準備啲文宣寄俾啲廢老睇，唔多嘅，幾百封咁啦。<br />\n<br />\n內容係文宣組嘅咁多位send 出黎嘅精品，我地已經一一print哂出黎俾啲廢老慢慢欣賞。<br />\n<br />\n我哋打算一得閒就寄一得閒寄，寄到佢哋局住一定要睇為止。等啲老人家可以欣賞到咁精彩絕倫嘅藝術品。Yeah!<br />\n<br />\n我大家有咩推介的文宣想我哋寄都可以留言話俾我哋聽㗎。有咩建議我哋都可以接受嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azqMAfx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazqMAfx.jpg&h=474047c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVNyZHd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVNyZHd.jpg&h=7b080136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bZtOAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bZtOAA.jpg&h=78469b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dwsjHf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dwsjHf.jpg&h=2f3461c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f95719974343eb9bd438e4944b9d91b4fb1f11a7","tid":1441142,"uid":81434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻你<br />\n有關聽日深水埗遊行 快入<br />\n<br />\n「 真 係 好 撚 想 同 你 哋 割 蓆 」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dfe55c8326cc0091df3162484d5d3f098ac362f6","tid":1441142,"uid":294954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"PUSH!"},{"pid":"08613417552dc2148f3b3f568ac56a3b0588f33a","tid":1441142,"uid":4285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score